      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我先把四个参与者列出来：User作为actor，WebUI、Server、Database作为participant。用户到WebUI的交互是「Add product to cart」对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
